sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Customer
    participant UI as Web App (TanStack)
    participant SF as Server Function
    participant DB as Postgres (RLS)
    actor A as Admin

    C->>UI: Browse /venues, apply filters
    UI->>DB: select venues where city/area/type
    DB-->>UI: venue rows
    UI-->>C: render cards

    C->>UI: Add to cart
    UI->>DB: insert cart_items (RLS: self)
    DB-->>UI: ok

    C->>UI: Go to /checkout
    UI->>SF: createBooking(cart)
    SF->>DB: load pricing_rules (active)
    DB-->>SF: rules
    SF->>SF: compute breakdown
    SF->>DB: insert bookings + booking_items (tx)
    DB-->>SF: booking.id
    SF-->>UI: booking summary
    UI-->>C: redirect to /my-bookings

    C->>UI: Submit payment proof
    UI->>DB: insert payment_proofs (status=pending)
    DB-->>UI: ok

    A->>UI: Open /admin/bookings
    UI->>DB: select payment_proofs where pending
    DB-->>UI: proofs
    A->>UI: Approve proof
    UI->>SF: approveProof(proofId)
    SF->>DB: insert transactions
    SF->>DB: update bookings.amount_paid, status
    SF->>DB: update payment_proofs.status=approved
    DB-->>SF: ok
    SF-->>UI: confirmation
    UI-->>C: booking shows Confirmed/Completed
